+Observations from reading `Git-Sync.psm1` (271 lines), `Sync-AllRepos-Hacker.ps1` (~340 lines), `build.ps1`, `Create-DesktopShortcut.ps1`, and `tests/Git-Sync.Tests.ps1`:
