+| Duplicate logic | None. Each git operation lives in exactly one helper. | ŌĆö |
+| Exception handling | Module uses `$ErrorActionPreference = 'Stop'` + `try/catch` consistently; UI script uses `Continue` so `-ContinueOnError` works. Correct. | ŌĆö |
+| Concurrency issues | Single-threaded by design. `ArrayList` (not generic `List[T]`) used for accumulation ŌĆö fine for the expected size. | Low |
+| Resource leaks | `Push-Location` / `Pop-Location` is in `try/finally` Ō£ģ. COM object in `Create-DesktopShortcut.ps1` is not `Marshal.ReleaseComObject`'d ŌĆö minor leak, GC reclaims it. | Low |
+| API contract violations | `Test-GitRepository` returns `[bool]`, no surprises. `Invoke-GitCommand` returns a hashtable shape ŌĆö documented in module help. | ŌĆö |
+| Null-safety | `Set-StrictMode -Version Latest` enforced. `[string]::IsNullOrWhiteSpace` checks present where it matters. | ŌĆö |
+| Performance | `Get-ChildItem` without `-Recurse` (correct, post-fix). Module imported once outside the per-repo loop. | ŌĆö |
+| Naming | Follows PowerShell verb-noun convention (`Get-`, `Test-`, `New-`, `Invoke-`); approved verbs only. | ŌĆö |
