+| `Git-Sync-Elevated.bat` | Self-elevating UAC variant of `Git-Sync.bat` | Group-policy-locked machines where you can't change CurrentUser policy |
+
+All four are pure batch ŌĆö they work in Command Prompt with no preconfiguration.
+
